# 第二十九章 参考文献

## 引用格式说明

本章引用的所有文献均采用APA第7版格式。这些文献涵盖了生成模型和扩散模型的核心理论、关键改进和应用实践。

---

## 核心参考文献

### 1. VAE (变分自编码器)

Kingma, D. P., & Welling, M. (2014). Auto-encoding variational Bayes. In *Proceedings of the 2nd International Conference on Learning Representations (ICLR)*. https://arxiv.org/abs/1312.6114

> **摘要**：本文提出了变分自编码器(VAE)，一种结合了深度学习和变分推断的生成模型。通过引入重参数化技巧，VAE可以使用随机梯度下降进行端到端训练。VAE为后续的生成模型奠定了理论基础。

---

### 2. GAN (生成对抗网络)

Goodfellow, I. J., Pouget-Abadie, J., Mirza, M., Xu, B., Warde-Farley, D., Ozair, S., Courville, A., & Bengio, Y. (2014). Generative adversarial nets. In *Advances in Neural Information Processing Systems (NeurIPS)*, 27, 2672-2680. https://arxiv.org/abs/1406.2661

> **摘要**：本文提出了生成对抗网络(GAN)，通过生成器和判别器的对抗训练来学习数据分布。GAN开启了深度学习生成模型的新时代，在图像生成领域产生了深远影响。

---

### 3. Normalizing Flow (标准化流)

Rezende, D. J., & Mohamed, S. (2015). Variational inference with normalizing flows. In *Proceedings of the 32nd International Conference on Machine Learning (ICML)*, 37, 1530-1538. https://arxiv.org/abs/1505.05770

> **摘要**：本文提出了标准化流，通过一系列可逆变换将简单分布映射到复杂分布。该方法允许精确计算似然值，为可追踪的生成模型提供了新的思路。

---

### 4. DDPM (去噪扩散概率模型)

Ho, J., Jain, A., & Abbeel, P. (2020). Denoising diffusion probabilistic models. In *Advances in Neural Information Processing Systems (NeurIPS)*, 33, 6840-6851. https://arxiv.org/abs/2006.11239

> **摘要**：本文提出了DDPM，将扩散模型改进为实用的图像生成器。通过重新参数化训练目标为噪声预测，DDPM实现了与GAN相媲美的图像质量，同时训练更加稳定。这是现代扩散模型的奠基之作。

---

### 5. Improved DDPM (改进的DDPM)

Nichol, A. Q., & Dhariwal, P. (2021). Improved denoising diffusion probabilistic models. In *Proceedings of the 38th International Conference on Machine Learning (ICML)*, 139, 8162-8171. https://arxiv.org/abs/2102.09672

> **摘要**：本文对DDPM进行了多项改进，包括学习的方差调度、余弦噪声调度和重要性采样，进一步提升了扩散模型的性能和采样速度。

---

### 6. DDIM (去噪扩散隐式模型)

Song, J., Meng, C., & Ermon, S. (2021). Denoising diffusion implicit models. In *Proceedings of the 9th International Conference on Learning Representations (ICLR)*. https://arxiv.org/abs/2010.02502

> **摘要**：本文提出了DDIM，通过非马尔可夫扩散过程实现了确定性和加速采样。DDIM将采样步骤从1000步减少到50步甚至更少，使扩散模型变得实用。

---

### 7. Score-Based Generative Modeling (基于分数的生成模型)

Song, Y., Sohl-Dickstein, J., Kingma, D. P., Kumar, A., Ermon, S., & Poole, B. (2021). Score-based generative modeling through stochastic differential equations. In *Proceedings of the 9th International Conference on Learning Representations (ICLR)*. https://arxiv.org/abs/2011.13456

> **摘要**：本文将扩散模型与随机微分方程(SDE)联系起来，提供了统一的理论框架。通过将前向和反向过程形式化为SDE，该工作连接了DDPM和分数匹配方法。

---

### 8. Classifier-Free Guidance (无分类器引导)

Ho, J., & Salimans, T. (2022). Classifier-free diffusion guidance. In *Proceedings of the NeurIPS 2021 Workshop on Deep Generative Models and Downstream Applications*. https://arxiv.org/abs/2207.12598

> **摘要**：本文提出了无分类器引导(CFG)，通过联合训练条件模型和无条件模型，无需额外的分类器即可实现高质量的条件生成。CFG已成为现代文本到图像生成模型的标准技术。

---

### 9. Latent Diffusion Model / Stable Diffusion (潜在扩散模型)

Rombach, R., Blattmann, A., Lorenz, D., Esser, P., & Ommer, B. (2022). High-resolution image synthesis with latent diffusion models. In *Proceedings of the IEEE/CVF Conference on Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (CVPR)*, 10684-10695. https://arxiv.org/abs/2112.10752

> **摘要**：本文提出了潜在扩散模型(LDM)，将扩散过程从像素空间转移到预训练VAE的潜在空间，显著降低了计算成本。Stable Diffusion是该工作的开源实现，深刻影响了AI生成艺术领域。

---

### 10. Diffusion Models Beat GANs (扩散模型超越GAN)

Dhariwal, P., & Nichol, A. (2021). Diffusion models beat GANs on image synthesis. In *Advances in Neural Information Processing Systems (NeurIPS)*, 34, 8780-8794. https://arxiv.org/abs/2105.05233

> **摘要**：本文展示了通过改进架构和引导技术，扩散模型在图像合成任务上超越了GAN。该工作确立了扩散模型作为生成模型新范式的地位。

---

## 补充阅读

### 扩散模型基础理论

Sohl-Dickstein, J., Weiss, E., Maheswaranathan, N., & Ganguli, S. (2015). Deep unsupervised learning using nonequilibrium thermodynamics. In *Proceedings of the 32nd International Conference on Machine Learning (ICML)*, 37, 2256-2265. https://arxiv.org/abs/1503.03585

> 扩散模型的开创性工作，从非平衡热力学角度提出了扩散概率模型。

### 一致性模型

Song, Y., Dhariwal, P., Chen, M., & Sutskever, I. (2023). Consistency models. In *Proceedings of the 40th International Conference on Machine Learning (ICML)*, 202, 32211-32252. https://arxiv.org/abs/2303.01469

> 提出了通过学习一致性映射实现单步或少步生成的新方法。

### 流匹配

Lipman, Y., Chen, R. T. Q., Ben-Hamu, H., Nickel, M., & Le, M. (2023). Flow matching for generative modeling. In *Proceedings of the 11th International Conference on Learning Representations (ICLR)*. https://arxiv.org/abs/2210.02747

> 提供了连接扩散模型和标准化流的统一框架，实现了更高效的训练和采样。

### 扩散Transformer

Peebles, W., & Xie, S. (2023). Scalable diffusion models with transformers. In *Proceedings of the IEEE/CVF International Conference on Computer Vision (ICCV)*, 4196-4206. https://arxiv.org/abs/2212.09748

> 将Transformer架构引入扩散模型，展示了优秀的扩展性。

